T1  - Hybrid Arrangements as Strategic Alliances: Theoretical Issues in Organizational Combinations
AU  - Borys, Bryan
AU  - Jemison, David B.
Y1  - 1989/04/01
PY  - 1989
DA  - 1989/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1989.4282106
